  "title": "非公開輪郭が前景に表示されるバグ",
  "created": 1778055328,
  "updated": 1778070451,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69faf89dc716d36481762622",
      "text": "非公開輪郭が前景に表示されるバグ",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778055328,
      "updated": 1778070451
    },
    {
      "id": "69faf8a00000000000e778b0",
      "text": "1. [https://gyazo.com/6149b5949b24d3b1ff66b70c9716ce1e]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778055328,
      "updated": 1778055358
    },
    {
      "id": "69faf8be0000000000e778b2",
      "text": "2. 任意の輪郭を引き入れる",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778055358,
      "updated": 1778055368
    },
    {
      "id": "69faf8c90000000000e778b3",
      "text": "3. [https://gyazo.com/45d77a5a97e794b22bb371687bc1649e]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778055370,
      "updated": 1778055395
    },
    {
      "id": "69faf8e30000000000e778b4",
      "text": "赤い四角の部分は隠しているが、クリックすると「権限なし」と表示される",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778055395,
      "updated": 1778055424
    },
    {
      "id": "69faf9000000000000e778b5",
      "text": "おそらく非公開輪郭が一覧に出てしまっている",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778055425,
      "updated": 1778056181
    },
    {
      "id": "69faf8a10000000000e778b1",
      "text": "少なくとも、リンクアドレスから輪番が確認できる状態のほか、輪郭名も確認できてしまう",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778055330,
      "updated": 1778056183
    },
    {
      "id": "69fafbf60000000000e778b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778056183,
      "updated": 1778056183
    },
    {
      "id": "69fafa370000000000e778b6",
      "text": "https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.AB64/B6AD",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778055735,
      "updated": 1778055735
    },
    {
      "id": "69fafa370000000000e778b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778055735,
      "updated": 1778055735
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb247e0000000000436cdc",
      "text": " 適当に直しておきます[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778066577,
      "updated": 1778066612
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb247e0000000000436cdd",
      "text": "  厳密にいうと，[デライト]には非公開輪郭というものはなく[未公開輪郭]は「まだあまり人目に晒したくない輪郭をゆるく非表示にする」程度の機能なので，今のところ優先度は低",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778066577,
      "updated": 1778067425
    },
    {
